<div class="container mt-5 ">
    <h1 class="mb-4  text-center">Payment on Delivery</h1>

    <p class="text-center">
        We offer a convenient Payment on Delivery (COD) option to make your shopping experience with Modum easy
        and hassle-free. Please review the details below:
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">1. How it Works</h2>
    <p>
        When you choose the COD option during checkout, you can pay for your order in cash when it is delivered to
        your specified address.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">2. Eligibility for COD</h2>
    <p>
        The COD option is available for orders meeting the following criteria:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Delivery address is within our COD service area.</li>
        <li>Order value is within the specified COD limit.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">3. Confirmation Call</h2>
    <p>
        Our customer support team may contact you to confirm your order and the COD payment option. Please ensure
        your contact details are accurate during checkout.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">4. Payment Process</h2>
    <p>
        When your order arrives, please have the exact amount ready for payment. Our delivery agent will collect
        the cash, provide a receipt, and complete the delivery.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">5. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
        If you have any questions or concerns regarding the COD option, please contact our customer support at <a href="/Footer/ContactUs">support@modum.com</a>
    </p>
</div>